The paper deals with combinatorial problems on hypergraphs, specifically finding perfect matchings in bipartite hypergraphs. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), and Graph Theory (cs.GT). However, since the paper focuses on hypergraphs and their properties, cs.DM and cs.DS are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also uses techniques that could be useful in other combinatorial problems on hypergraphs, which further supports the possibility of it belonging to cs.CG, cs.CC, or cs.GT.
